        <item>
            <title>1.0.24</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new</h3>
<ul>
<li>Verification codes in incoming emails now appear right in the notification, with a "Copy Code" button — no need to open the email.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Bug fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Searching with the unread-only filter active no longer hides matches silently — the results header now shows how many results the filter is hiding.</li>
<li>Fixed "1 results" pluralization in the search header.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
