        <item>
            <title>1.0.23</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new</h3>
<ul>
<li>When forwarding an email, Normal Mail now offers to carry over the original message's attachments.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Bug fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Quick Look no longer re-opens an attachment when you press the space bar in another window.</li>
<li>Attachments in the compose window now wrap onto multiple rows instead of being cut off when there are several of them.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
